text: Andrés Mauricio Copete Ceballos (born October 29, 1983) is a Colombian footballer who plays for Parrillas One. ==Club career== He made his debut in Honduras for Victoria against Deportes Savio on 2 August 2008, scoring the winning goal. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:People from Valle del Cauca Department Category:Colombian footballers Category:C.D.
